<span id="freeTextContainer16125266136910679812">This book was so long and it didn&apos;t come in large print. I read three letters- one in the beginning, one in the middle and one at the end. The writing was good and it seemed interesting but I don&apos;t know enough about Flannery O&apos;Connor&apos;s life and times and works to be interested in all the letters. I put the book down.<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText16125266136910679812" style="display:none">This book was so long and it didn't come in large print. I read three letters- one in the beginning, one in the middle and one at the end. The writing was good and it seemed interesting but I don't know enough about Flannery O'Connor's life and times and works to be interested in all the letters. I put the book down.<br /></span>
