        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3856233196" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1312962326310733256">I decided to read this book because I read Flannery O&apos;Connor&apos;s short stories. To be honest, I had a difficult time with them. I am a Roman Catholic and wanted to understand her symbolism better. These letters really help. <br/><br/>If you&apos;re interested in reading Flannery O&apos;Connor&apos;s works, I suggest you start with her letters. They explain who she was and gives insight to her life. <br/><br/>I plan to go back and read all her fiction.</span>
  <span id="freeText1312962326310733256" style="display:none">I decided to read this book because I read Flannery O'Connor's short stories. To be honest, I had a difficult time with them. I am a Roman Catholic and wanted to understand her symbolism better. These letters really help. <br /><br />If you're interested in reading Flannery O'Connor's works, I suggest you start with her letters. They explain who she was and gives insight to her life. <br /><br />I plan to go back and read all her fiction.</span>
